author: Xbox
description:
Discover how FEARLESS you truly are during Overwatch 2 x LE SSERAFIM.

Get ready for a new and vibrant collaboration with returning K-Pop sensation, LE SSERAFIM. Enjoy dazzling new skins that are sure to turn heads and new emotes for when the music calls to you.

Before their arrival in-game, join us for a closer look at the new skins and watch LE SSERAFIM’s newest music video during our Overwatch 2 x LE SSERAFIM Livestream Event happening March 17 at 8:30pm PT.

Take centerstage when Overwatch 2 x LE SSERAFIM arrives in-game for a limited time Mar 18.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
